$Id: INSTALL,v 1.3 2001/11/01 22:36:53 mysidia Exp $

Dependencies: libevent.
Select/Polling library
http://www.monkey.org/~provos/libevent-0.3d.tar.gz

Dependencies: adns.
Asychronous/Advanced Resolver library
http://www.chiark.greenend.org.uk/~ian/adns/

1. Run configure with appropriate options
2. Run make (build)
3. Run make install with appropriate privileges
